   Baltimore needed it because Minnesota came back with a run in
the bottom half against reliever Buddy Groom. Guzman hit his second
double of the game, took third on a groundout and scored when Ron
Coomer reached on a throwing error by Lewis at shortstop.
</P>
<P>
