rib cage muscle, 22 games with a back injury that sidelined him
from June 14 to July 2, and 34 games since Aug. 1 with lower back
inflammation.
</P>
<P>
   Castilla, 33, hit 203 homers over seven seasons in Colorado
before being dealt by the Rockies last December. He has hit .223
with six homers and 39 RBIs in 71 games this season.
